    <item>
      <title>央行行长称利比亚接近达成石油协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/libya-moving-closer-to-oil-deal-central-banker-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚央行行长身处欧佩克成员国政府权力斗争的中心，他表示，双方似乎即将达成协议，以解决争端并刺激恢复至关重要的石油生产。彭博社的 Anthony DiPaola 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/libya-moving-closer-to-oil-deal-central-banker-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济担忧导致欧洲股市科技股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球经济健康状况的担忧削弱了本周晚些时候美国关键就业数据公布前的市场人气，欧洲股市下跌。科技股下跌，追随 Nvidia Corp. 隔夜下跌的脚步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
