      <title>西波隆称欧洲央行政策面临过于严格的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/cipollone-sees-risk-that-ecb-stance-could-become-too-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员皮耶罗·西波洛内表示，欧洲央行不应长期维持过高利率，因为这样做可能会损害经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/cipollone-sees-risk-that-ecb-stance-could-become-too-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
